/_site/
/.quarto/
*.html.bak
.DS_Store
*__pycache__*

# Rendered HTML belongs in _site/. Stray .html in the source tree are
# single-file `quarto render` artifacts — never commit them. (The design
# mockup is the one intentional exception.)
*.html
!design/mockup.html

# team/index.qmd is generated from openpipeline core at render time
# (see scripts/generate_team.py). Generated subdirs are ignored, but the
# roster overlay (maintainers/advisors/sponsors source) must be tracked.
/team/*/
!/team/roster/
